cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "Ukrainian Poetry Generator: Hybrid LLM + Rule-Based System for Formal Control of Meter and Rhyme"
abstract: >
  Hybrid system for automated generation of Ukrainian classical poetry that
  separates semantic generation (LLM) from formal validation (rule-based
  meter + rhyme algorithms). Includes IPA-based phonetic rhyme similarity,
  syllabotonic meter validation with classical prosodic tolerances, semantic
  RAG, metric-rhyme few-shot retrieval, an iterative feedback loop, and a
  full ablation harness for measuring each component's contribution.
